Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:16.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon sealed away in lunar prison
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:20.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Life will go on in the kingdom below
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:25.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All is set right in the world for a season
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:29.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Til her release when this story is closed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:32.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The stars will aid in her escape
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:35.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Return to where the battle raged
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:38.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The elements will wash away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:41.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The darkness and the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:45.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My little ponies the horror has ended
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:50.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Luna will pay for the crime she has done
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:55.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don’t let her sins fill your mind up with hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:59.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forgiveness is all I can ask of you now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:02.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For the future is bright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:04.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Golden age within sight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:08.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If you let love lead the way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:13.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now the sunrise lifts us up from the dark~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:17.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The dawn bringing light, bringing hope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:21.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We will rebuild for our spirit is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:31.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And Harmony will be restored~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:28.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Listen now my children
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:31.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For the meaning of her fall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:34.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A heart that’s left abandoned
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:38.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Causes sadness in us all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:41.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So love your fellow ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:45.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Show a kindness unrestrained
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:54.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And Harmony will follow you for all~ of your days~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:30.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now the sunrise lifts us up from the dark~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.14,0:24:34.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The dawn bringing light, bringing hope
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:39.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We will rebuild for our spirit is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.98,0:24:51.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And Harmony will be restored~